dict.string: Tracco is an iOS app that calculates users' carbon emissions and gives recommendations to other transportation modes that has far more efficient in terms of carbon emission and cost. This is a solution to the challenge of helping people reduce their transportation carbon emissions by giving them information about the emission produced by their chosen transportation, logging users' carbon emission, and providing information on alternative public transportation with lower cost and lower carbon emission transportation.
Images provided on onboarding, alerts, home, profile, and history pages are from Storyset (http://storyset.com)
